  <name>Cavasik</name>
  <summary>Audio visualizer based on CAVA.</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Cavasik is an audio visualizer based on CAVA with customizable LibAdwaita interface.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Has 4 drawing modes!</li>
      <li>Set a single color or up to 10 colors for a linear gradient for the background and the foreground.</li>
      <li>Configure smoothing, noise reduction and a few other CAVA settings.</li>
      <li>Change colors dynamically from other applications using a DBus interface.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.TheWisker.Cavasik.desktop</launchable>
